... styling for diffs ... */\n}\n```\n\n### File Paths Summary\n\n- **Web Handler (API endpoints)**: `/workspace/internal/adapters/web/handler.go`\n- **Project Detail Template**: `/workspace/internal/adapters/web/templates/project_detail.html`\n- **Styling**: `/workspace/internal/adapters/web/static/style.css`\n- **Layout Template**: `/workspace/internal/adapters/web/templates/layout.html`"}],"totalDurationMs":27974,"totalTokens":51023,"totalToolUseCount":20,"usage":{"input_tokens":4,"cache_creation_input_tokens":283,"cache_read_input_tokens":49663,"output_tokens":1073,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":283},"inference_geo":"","iterations":[],"speed":"standard"}}}
